---

<PageLayout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
>
  
  <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-4">
    <Breadcrumbs 
      items={[
        { name: "Home", url: "/" },
        { name: "Service Areas", url: "/service-areas" },
        { name: "Markham" }
      ]}
    />
  </div>

<!-- Location Hero -->
  <Hero 
    title="Waterproofing Markham"
    subtitle="Professional basement waterproofing and foundation repair serving all Markham neighborhoods. 25-year warranty, free inspection."
    primaryCTA={{ text: "Get Free Markham Quote", href: "/free-inspection" }}
    secondaryCTA={{ text: "Call: 437-545-0067", href: "tel:437-545-0067" }}
    backgroundImage="/images/dryspace_hero_desktop.webp"
    badge="Serving Markham"
  />

  <!-- Internal Links -->
  <section class="py-8 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <InternalLinks category="location" currentPage="markham" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <Stats />

  <!-- Local Information Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">WATERPROOFING SERVICES IN MARKHAM</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg  max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
            Markham's transformation from rural farmland to Ontario's largest suburban municipality created unique waterproofing challenges. Rapid development over naturally high water table areas, combined with dense clay soils that retain moisture, means many 25-35 year old homes now face foundation issues. Our team specializes in both the engineering challenges of Rouge River watershed properties and the cultural sensitivity required for Markham's significant heritage preservation needs.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 p-6 mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Markham's Development Challenge</h3>
            <p class="text-cyan-700 text-sm">
              Converting farmland to residential communities often overlooked natural drainage patterns. Fields that managed seasonal water through crops and natural grade now concentrate runoff around homes, creating foundation pressure that wasn't anticipated in original construction.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200  p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase">MARKHAM QUICK FACTS</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600 ">
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Population</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">338,000</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Average Home Age</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">25-35 YEARS</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Annual Rainfall</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">815MM ANNUALLY</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Frost Line</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">1.2 METERS</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Flood Risk</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">LOW TO MODERATE</span>
              </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-navy-900 border-2 border-slate-200  p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase">MARKHAM'S UNIQUE CHALLENGES</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300">
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Dense clay soils create extreme hydrostatic pressure</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Rouge River watershed maintains high groundwater</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Rapid subdivision development over former farmland</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Cultural heritage buildings require sensitive approaches</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Seasonal flooding from Rouge River tributaries</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Subdivision drainage interdependencies</span>
              </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Markham Communities & Their Water Challenges</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Each Markham community faces distinct challenges based on development era, soil conditions, and watershed location:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-4 border border-slate-100 rounded">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">UNIONVILLE (Heritage Core)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Historic buildings, cultural heritage preservation, traditional construction</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 border border-slate-100 rounded">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">MILLIKEN & CORNELL (New Development)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Former farmland, high water table, subdivision drainage challenges</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 border border-slate-100 rounded">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">ROUGE RIVER CORRIDOR</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Seasonal flooding, wetland proximity, environmental restrictions</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 border border-slate-100 rounded">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">BERCZY & CACHET (Premium Developments)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Clay soil challenges, finished basements, high property values</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {["Unionville","Milliken","Cornell","Berczy","Cachet","Rouge","Wismer","Angus Glen","Box Grove"].map((neighborhood) => (
              <span class="border-2 border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 text-sm">
                {neighborhood}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <Services />

  <!-- Location Features -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">WHY CHOOSE DRYSPACE IN MARKHAM</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Local expertise combined with industry-leading warranties and service
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Highlighted Features -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        {locationFeatures.filter(f => f.highlight).map((feature) => (
          <div class="bg-amber-500 border-2 border-slate-700 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase">{feature.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-900">{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <!-- Regular Features -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {locationFeatures.filter(f => !f.highlight).map((feature) => (
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 p-6 hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase">{feature.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <Process />


  <!-- Location Image Showcase -->
  <LocationImageShowcase city="Markham" />

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <Testimonials />

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">MARKHAM WATERPROOFING FAQS</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Common questions from Markham homeowners</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        {locationFAQs.map((faq, index) => (
          <details class="mb-4 border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase pr-4">{faq.question}</h3>
                <span class="text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0 text-2xl">+</span>
              </div>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-0">
              <p class="text-slate-600">{faq.answer}</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">SECURE YOUR MARKHAM INVESTMENT</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">
          From heritage preservation in Unionville to new development challenges throughout the Rouge watershed, our Markham specialists provide solutions that respect both cultural heritage and modern engineering requirements.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/free-inspection"
            class="bg-amber-500 text-black px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors uppercase"
          >
            Get Watershed-Specific Assessment
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/contact"
            class="border-2 border-white text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors uppercase"
          >
            Heritage Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center text-cyan-400">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase">24/7 Emergency Service Available</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(localBusinessSchema)}>
<BreadcrumbSchema items={[{name: 'Home', url: '/'}, {name: 'Locations', url: '/locations'}, {name: 'Markham'}]} />
